Title: [ANN][Token Sale] NOBAR - The Complete Crypto Commerce
Body: One of the biggest challenges that we have, is that due to the wide fluctuations of the values,  users have started treating cryptocurrencies and crypto tokens as assets. The dominating  tendency is to “short sell” to make a short-term profit. This defeats the main purpose of a currency, which is to work as a medium fortransactions.  Most of the cryptocurrencies and crypto tokens currently present in the world are currently used for only speculative trading. Imagine US Dollar as a currency which is only used to be traded against other currencies of the world, for the hope of making profits out of the trading. This hypothetical situation is being realized in the crypto world which will ultimately lead to a collapse of the market.  NOBAR promises to give the power back to the users. By using the token as a mean to purchase and sell products, the project want to establish NBR token as an appropriate replacement for traditional currencies.

Author: Gustafio
Title: [ANN][Token Sale] NOBAR - The Complete Crypto Commerce
Body: Wanted to share a great answer the Nobar CEO, Joyjit Bhowmick answered Suumit Shah (ICO reviewer) in Icobench.   Suumit Shar: "The problem is not paying using various methods, problem is getting users to transact. How you are planning to fight with companies like Amazon?"  Joyjit Bhowmick responds: "I do agree with you on the point that the problem is getting users to transact. That is one of the main problems in the crypto world that we are trying to solve as speculative trading on exchanges is the only activity people are doing with cryptocurrency and crypto tokens. Compared to exchange platforms, the number of platforms supporting commercial activities with crypto payment is negligible. There is only a handful supporting any kind of real-world application. Not to mention that their supported activities are very limited if we compare them to the whole e-commerce world. Therefore, there is no way for people to use their cryptocurrency other than trading with fiat currencies. That is why we are building platforms where a wide range of commercial activities can be performed.  How do we plan to compete against Amazon? Let us take a look at it with numbers. The global nominal GDP is almost 80 trillion USD whereas the cryptocurrency market value is below 300 billion USD as of now which is 0.3%. It clearly states that the crypto market is still very small in the aspect of being a universal means of payment. Also, the e-commerce and digital payment industry have a combined value of 4 trillion USD which is 5% of the global GDP. This 4 trillion USD is a combined number of many e-commerce sites like Amazon. Alibaba, eBay etc. However, each of them is following a different business model and supports different kinds of activities. The platforms that we are developing will encompass B2B, B2C, C2C, C2B, Jobs, Ads and POS. None of Amazon, eBay, Alibaba or any other platforms encompasses such variety of activities. Such robust platforms are needed in the crypto world to increase the usage commonality of cryptocurrencies so that people can start to use it on a daily basis rather than doing only speculative trading. Additionally, none of the established e-commerce platforms accepts crypto payments. So even if the crypto market is still relatively small, along with speculative trading we need real-world applications of crypto."

Author: Joyjit
Title: [ANN][Token Sale] NOBAR - The Complete Crypto Commerce
Body: Yes, there are other similar projects with bits and pieces of what we are doing. However, there is no project until now which is unifying all of these activities into one unified platform. So NBR token holders can enjoy engaging with different commercial and transactional activities with just one token.  What happens with the other projects is their associated activities are limited and if you want to engage in some other activities with any of those tokens, then you have to exchange it with some other tokens and only then you can use it on your desired other platform. This creates a hassle and some transactional losses. Not to mention limited facilities cannot create a large enough usage commonality which NOBAR is capable of.  Please do not hesitate to reach out to us for any further queries.

Author: Joyjit
Title: [ANN][Token Sale] NOBAR - The Complete Crypto Commerce
Body: Yes, there are other similar projects with bits and pieces of what we are doing. However, there is no project until now which is unifying all of these activities into one unified platform. So NBR token holders can enjoy engaging with different commercial and transactional activities with just one token.  What happens with the other projects is their associated activities are limited and if you want to engage in some other activities with any of those tokens, then you have to exchange it with some other tokens and only then you can use it on your desired other platform. This creates a hassle and some transactional losses. Not to mention limited facilities cannot create a large enough usage commonality which NOBAR is capable of.  Please do not hesitate to reach out to us for any further queries.

Author: Joyjit
Title: [ANN][Token Sale] NOBAR - The Complete Crypto Commerce
Body: Yes, if we look at the roadmap then we can see we have plans on listing NBR token on exchanges on August immediately after our tokensale.

Author: Joyjit
Title: [ANN][Token Sale] NOBAR - The Complete Crypto Commerce
Body: Thank you very much for asking two important questions  NOBAR platform is bringing B2B, B2C, C2C, C2B, Ads, Jobs and POS (Point of Sale) payment activities into one singular platform. Therefore, you can perform any kind of commercial activities on the platform through the native "Crypto Commerce" function and even pay at any grocery store or any physical with the "Shop-App" function. Moreover, NBR token is two decimal which is convenient for regular use.  Firstly, NOBAR platform is substantial for all your online commercial and transactional activities. There are no platform till now which is offering all these activities into one platform. Therefore, the users of other platforms have to exchange their tokens everytime they want to engage in other activities other than any activity their token and platform supports. This creates a hassle for the users and not to mention some transactional losses. If you use NOBAR platform, you will face no such problems. Besides, there is a loyalty program which benefits frequent users on the platform.  I hope the above is substantial for your queries. Please do not hesitate to reach out to us for any more questions. Thanks and Best Regards
